### Create doctor (one-time)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Dr. Priya Menon",
    "age": 34,
    "phoneNumber": "9000000001",
    "password": "Doctor@123",
    "passwordConfirm": "Doctor@123"
}

### Doctor login (grab jwt cookie from response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/doctors/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phoneNumber": "9000000001",
    "password": "Doctor@123"
}

